{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Note:</strong> Headphones are highly recommended. In co-op mode, a microphone is essential for voice chat. It triggers the ghost. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Work Together!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this demo, you and a friend are stuck in two connected houses. You need to solve unique mysterious puzzles together to escape!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/DemoRotateFrame_600_338.png?t=1737433588\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Evade the Entity!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During the demo, a blind entity roams the shadows, going back and forth between the houses trying to catch you. You must avoid it at all costs!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/DemoAvoidGG2_Small.gif?t=1737433588\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Be Quiet!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The entity in the demo might be blind but it hears EVERYTHING! Whenever you hear it, you have to be very quiet or it will come for you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/DemoSafe_Small.gif?t=1737433588\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Save Your Friend!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If the entity captures your friend in the demo, they will be imprisoned in a cage. You must act quickly to free them before the entity catches you too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/SaveYourFriendTrimmed.gif?t=1737433588\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Escape together!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you and your friend escape the entity's grasp before time runs out in this demo adventure?</p