. You must act quickly to free them before the entity catches you too!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/extras/SaveYourFriendTrimmed.gif?t=1737433588\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Escape together!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can you and your friend escape the entity's grasp before time runs out in this demo adventure?</p>","developers":["Twisted Realm"],"fullgame":{"appid":"2976110","name":"Separated"},"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110110/header.jpg?t=1737433588","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257041702,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041702/movie480.mp4?t=1733230647","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041702/movie_max.mp4?t=1733230647"},"name":"Game Teaser","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257041702/fd04c9914d62b6687dce24c48fc8997d8acb2e0f/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1733230647","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041702/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1733230647","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257041702/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1733230647"}}],"name":"Separated Demo","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating 